# Documentation Content Folder

Place your markdown documentation files here.
They will be validated and ingested into the documentation system.

## File Format

Each file must have YAML frontmatter:

```markdown
---
title: "Your Title"
slug: "your-slug"
category: "getting-started"
status: draft | review | published
---

## Overview

Your content here...
```

## Commands

- Validate: `python manage.py ingest_docs docs/content --validate-only`
- Import: `python manage.py ingest_docs docs/content`
- Publish: `python manage.py ingest_docs docs/content --publish`
- Template: `python manage.py ingest_docs --template guide`
